quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  2,225,khuda tumhari laghu qasmon par tum se muwakhza nah kere ga. lekin jo kasmain tum qasad dili se khao ge un par muwakhza kere ga. aur khuda bakhsnay wala Burdbar hai
  2,226,jo log apni aurton ke paas jaane se qasam khalin un ko chaar mahinay taq intzaar karna chahiye. agar ( is arsay mein qasam se ) rujoo karlen to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  2,227,aur agar Talaq ka iradah karlen to bhi khuda santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
  2,228,aur Talaq wali aurtain teen haiz taq apni tain rokay rahen. aur agar woh khuda aur roz qayamat par imaan rakhti hain to un ka jaaiz nahi ke khuda ne jo kuch un ke shikam mein pedakiya hai is ko chupayen. aur un ke khawand agar phir muwafiqat chahain to is ( muddat ) mein woh un ko apni zojiat mein le lainay ke ziyada haqdaar hain. aur aurton ka haq ( mardon par ) waisa hi hai jaisay dastoor ke mutabiq ( mardon ka haq ) aurton par hai. Albata mardon ko aurton par fazeelat hai. aur khuda ghalib ( aur ) sahib hikmat hai
  2,229,Talaq ( sirf ) dobaar hai ( yani jab do dafaa Talaq day di jaye to ) phir ( aurton ko ) ya to ba-tareeq shaista ( nikah mein ) rehne dena ya bhalai ke sath chore dena. aur yeh jaaiz nahi ke jo mohar tum un ko day chuke ho is mein se kuch wapas le lau. haan agar zan o shohar ko khauf ho ke woh khuda ki hado ko qaim nahi rakh saken ge to agar aurat ( khawand ke haath se ) rihayi panay ke badlay mein kuch day daaley to dono par kuch gunah nahi. yeh khuda ki ( muqarrar ki hui ) hade hain un se bahar nah niklana. aur jo log khuda ki hado se bahar nikal jayen ge woh gunehgaar hon ge
  2,230,phir agar shohar ( do tlaqon ke baad teesri ) Talaq aurat ko day day to is ke baad jab taq aurat kisi dosray shakhs se nikah nah karle is ( pehlay shohar ) par halal nah hogi. haan agar dosra khawand bhi Talaq day day aur aurat aur pehla khawand phir aik dosray ki taraf rujoo karlen to un par kuch gunah nahi bashart e kay dono yaqeen karen ke khuda ki hado ko qaim rakh saken ge aur yeh khuda ki hade hain un ko woh un logon ke liye bayan farmata hai jo Danish rakhtay hain
